				<section>
					<h3>Introduction</h3>
					<p>Parallel to the soil moisture calculation, an estimate of the uncertainty of the soil moisture retrieval is determined by rules
					of <b>error propagation</b>.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h3>Error Propagation I</h3>
					<ul><li>determination of the noise level of the backscatter measurements
					<li>Assumptions:
					<ul><li type="circle">all three beams observe the same region
					<li type="circle">the fore- and aft-beam have the same incidence angle and are thus comparable (as long as there are no azimuthal 
					effects)</ul>
				</section>
				
				<section>
					<h3>Error Propagation II</h3>
					<ul><li>The difference &delta; should be 0:
					<br><img data-src="./lecture_material/L7_uncertainty/eq_2-17.png" style="width:200px;height:auto;" >
					<li>its variance should be twice the variance of one of the beams (assuming independent measurements)
					<br><img data-src="./lecture_material/L7_uncertainty/eq_2-18.png" style="width:200px;height:auto;" >
					<li>Estimate of the standard deviation of the backscatter &sigma;<sup>0</sup> (the so-called ESD):
					<br><img data-src="./lecture_material/L7_uncertainty/eq_2-19.png" style="width:200px;height:auto;" >
				</section>

				<section>
					<h3>Error Propagation III</h3>
					<p>A noise estimate of the normalised backscatter &sigma;<sup>0</sup>(40Â°, t) is obtained by:
					<br><img data-src="./lecture_material/L7_uncertainty/eq_2-20.png" style="width:700px;height:auto;" >
					<br><small><i>i...the individual fore-, mid- and aft-beam measurements of the backscatter triplet</i></small></p>
					
				</section>

				<section>
					<h3>Uncertainty estimate of the soil moisture retrieval</h3>
					<ul><li>no simple general expression for the noise estimate of the dry and wet reference
					<li>noise estimate of wet reference is simpler because the wet crossover angle and the reference incidence angle are 
					both equal to 40 degrees
					<li>final equation for an uncertainty estimate of the soil moisture retrieval:</ul>
					<br><img data-src="./lecture_material/L7_uncertainty/eq_2-23.png" style="width:600px;height:auto;" >
				</section>

				<section>
					<h3>SCAT noise from error propagation</h3>
